{"tid":1849873,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好帶金屬汽球搭港鐵","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T03:32:00.000Z","uid":137424,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b27c0ed00bfdd0259f1c0bf315019e0f02f8371b","tid":1849873,"uid":137424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"頭先經過大埔，見到好多一家大細拎住個金屬汽球入閘搭港鐵。咁樣做好危險，好多小朋友揸唔實就會唔小心飛咗個汽球上架空電纜導致跳掣，成條鐵就會停駛。呢排有好多人仲要返工或香港人由大陸返香港避肺炎，所以好多人仲要搭鐵。所以港鐵已經成日叫人唔好帶金屬汽球入閘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BP3bHLm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBP3bHLm.jpg&h=69c979d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3008e5e6a2a5c63d451cbf40686323bdb5895874","tid":1849873,"uid":137424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe84c529ab1f856ea0f90b9a785f19b58bae601","tid":1849873,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你有冇諗過 如果停左,  成班人困住喺車廂會點 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d52ae5dd8b62f6e5681dc0954cb233438110e05","tid":1849873,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe84c529ab1f856ea0f90b9a785f19b58bae601","tid":1849873,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁你有冇諗過 如果停左,  成班人困住喺車廂會點 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41e0fa2d73c47656fd133faf7163f59d581041c","tid":1849873,"uid":50757,"like":0,"di